t; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-st=
yle: solid; background-color: #ccc;">clearinghouses and brokers</a>. Anothe=
r difference between decentralized finance and traditional finance is that =
DeFi tends to be sort of flat =E2=80=94=C2=A0all sorts of customers trade d=
irectly with exchanges, etc. =E2=80=94=C2=A0while tradfi tends to be sort o=
f hierarchical, with customers trading through brokers who trade through cl=
earing brokers who trade through clearinghouses, etc.</em></p><p style=3D"m=
argin: 16px 0;"><em>[3] This is oversimplified; the statutory straddle rule=
s are in <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/28128683.=
261603/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubGF3LmNvcm5lbGwuZWR1L3VzY29kZS90ZXh0LzI2LzEwOTI/607f=
